{"tid":294765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學家發現火星大小神祕物體　有望成為第10大行星","createTime":"2017-06-23T08:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T03:47:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b3705b7a0b78fabfcba73e10ef61040e3d9d0c","tid":294765,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:47:51.000Z","msg":"2017-06-23 11:30<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170623/_2017062311301652347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170623%2F_2017062311301652347.jpg&h=f11c0c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國研究人員在古柏帶 (Kuiper Belt) 附近發現一顆火星大小的神祕物體，科學家宣稱這和過去不斷謠傳存在的「第9行星」(Planet 9) 不同，有望成為太陽系第10大行星。<br />\n<br />\n亞利桑那大學 (University of Arizona) 的月球和行星實驗室科學家Kate Volk和Renu Malhotra透過研究古柏帶，發現這顆距離地球約55天文單位的物體，這個位置比「第九行星」被估計的位置稍微進了一些。它的大小介乎於火星和地球之間，他們在研究古柏帶造成時發現不尋常的重力拉力，因此推測該處有這個神秘物體。<br />\n<br />\n去年發表的第9行星研究報告的作者之一、加利福尼亞理工學院天文學家Konstantin Batygin認為，不應立即認定這顆物體就是第10行星。因為太陽系中有許多物體。又指這顆新發現的神祕物體相當小，有可能無法達到行星的標準，目前它也尚未被人觀測到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/934473/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F934473%2F&d=qkK6BSb8oTDgM2Fg%2BRYRtxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=be8438a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F934473%2F&h=73fa6f2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/934473/</a>"},{"pid":"dfa34d5c42a0632dabf1f5c7cf63428f8298f4f0","tid":294765,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398c80d5015fd3bc7bc3cee8b98f520c04fbb63c","tid":294765,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"第九都未肯定到而家岩岩發現的神秘物體就有望做第十?"},{"pid":"758d68870c42828aaacd5f142